---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HumanRedirect from '../../components/HumanRedirect.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Shivrajsinh Zala | Frontend Developer Rajkot" description="Learn about Shivrajsinh Zala, a Rajkot frontend developer specializing in React, WordPress, Webflow, Shopify, and brutalist design.">
    <Fragment slot="head">
<meta name="author" content="Shivrajsinh Zala">
<meta property="og:title" content="About Shivrajsinh Zala | Frontend Developer">
<meta property="og:image" content="https://shivrajsinh.in/assets/images/shivrajsinh-zala-frontend-developer-rajkot.webp">
<meta property="og:url" content="https://shivrajsinh.in/blog/about-shivrajsinh-zala-frontend-developer">
<meta property="og:type" content="profile">
<meta property="og:description" content="Learn about Shivrajsinh Zala, a professional Frontend Developer based in Rajkot, Gujarat, specializing in React, WordPress, Webflow, Shopify, and Brutalist Design.">
<meta property="og:site_name" content="Shivrajsinh Zala">
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
<meta name="twitter:title" content="About Shivrajsinh Zala | Frontend Developer in Rajkot, Gujarat">
<meta name="twitter:description" content="Learn about Shivrajsinh Zala, a professional Frontend Developer based in Rajkot, Gujarat, specializing in React, WordPress, Webflow, Shopify, and Brutalist Design.">
<meta name="twitter:image" content="https://shivrajsinh.in/assets/images/shivrajsinh-zala-frontend-developer-rajkot.webp">
<script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "ProfilePage",
      "mainEntity": {
        "@type": "Person",
        "@id": "https://shivrajsinh.in/#person",
        "name": "Shivrajsinh Zala",
        "jobTitle": "Frontend Developer",
        "url": "https://shivrajsinh.in",
        "image": "https://shivrajsinh.in/assets/images/shivrajsinh-zala-frontend-developer-rajkot.webp",
        "sameAs": [
          "https://github.com/shivrajsinhzala",
          "https://www.linkedin.com/in/shivrajsinh-zala/",
          "https://www.instagram.com/shivrajsinh.sh"
        ],
        "address": {
          "@type": "PostalAddress",
          "addressLocality": "Rajkot",
          "addressRegion": "Gujarat",
          "addressCountry": "India"
        }
      }
    }
    </script>
    </Fragment>

    <main class="relative z-10 pt-24 pb-20 px-4">
        <article class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 md:p-12 lg:p-20 mt-12 shadow-[16px_16px_0_0_#000] relative">
            
            <div class="w-full aspect-square md:aspect-video brutal-border overflow-hidden mb-8 bg-brutal-gray relative">
                <img src="/assets/images/shivrajsinh-zala-frontend-developer-rajkot.webp" alt="Shivrajsinh Zala, Frontend Developer in Rajkot" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 bg-[#00FF88] text-black font-mono font-bold text-xs px-3 py-1 brutal-border border-r-0 border-b-0">SHIVRAJSINH ZALA</div>
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-[0.85] uppercase hover-word-container">
                Who is Shivrajsinh Zala?
                <span class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-4 bg-brutal-yellow -z-10 opacity-50 skew-x-12"></span>
            </h1>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 font-mono text-sm mb-10 border-b-2 border-black pb-6">
                <span class="bg-brutal-black text-white px-2 py-1">PROFILE</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500">RAJKOT, GUJARAT, INDIA</span>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-xl md:prose-2xl max-w-none font-sans 
            prose-headings:font-black prose-headings:tracking-tighter prose-headings:uppercase 
            prose-h2:text-4xl prose-h2:md:text-5xl prose-h2:border-b-4 prose-h2:border-black prose-h2:pb-4 prose-h2:mt-16 prose-h2:bg-transparent prose-h2:text-black
            prose-h3:text-2xl prose-h3:bg-brutal-pink prose-h3:text-white prose-h3:inline-block prose-h3:px-4 prose-h3:py-2 prose-h3:border-4 prose-h3:border-black prose-h3:shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#000]
            prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-p:mb-8 prose-p:font-medium
            prose-a:bg-brutal-cyan prose-a:text-black prose-a:px-1 prose-a:border-b-4 prose-a:border-black hover:prose-a:bg-brutal-yellow hover:prose-a:translate-y-1 prose-a:transition-all prose-a:no-underline
            prose-blockquote:border-l-8 prose-blockquote:border-brutal-pink prose-blockquote:bg-brutal-gray prose-blockquote:p-6 prose-blockquote:font-mono prose-blockquote:text-lg prose-blockquote:shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000]
            prose-ul:border-4 prose-ul:border-black prose-ul:p-8 prose-ul:bg-brutal-yellow/20 prose-ul:shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000] prose-li:font-bold prose-li:marker:text-brutal-pink
            prose-img:border-4 prose-img:border-black prose-img:shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000]
            first-letter:text-7xl first-letter:font-black first-letter:text-white first-letter:mr-4 first-letter:float-left first-letter:leading-[0.8] first-letter:border-4 first-letter:border-black first-letter:pt-2 first-letter:pb-0 first-letter:px-3 first-letter:bg-brutal-pink first-letter:shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#000]
            ">
                
                <p class="text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8">
                    <strong>Shivrajsinh Zala</strong> is a highly skilled Frontend Developer and Web Designer based in Rajkot, Gujarat. With a passion for building lightning-fast, highly interactive, and visually stunning digital experiences, Shivrajsinh has established himself as an expert in modern web technologies including React, Webflow, WordPress, and Shopify.
                </p>

                <h2>Professional Background</h2>
                <p>
                    Based in the vibrant city of Rajkot, Shivrajsinh Zala combines a deep understanding of core engineering principles with an eye for cutting-edge design trends—specifically "Brutalist" web design. He specializes in creating websites that break away from corporate templates, providing brands with unique, unforgettable digital identities.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Beyond just writing code, Shivrajsinh brings extensive experience in Digital Marketing and Amazon Product Listing optimization. This dual expertise means every website he builds isn't just visually impressive; it's architected from the ground up for SEO and high conversion rates.
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 my-10">
                    <div class="brutal-border bg-brutal-gray p-4 flex-1 shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#000]">
                        <h4 class="font-mono font-bold m-0 uppercase">Core Expertise</h4>
                        <ul class="font-mono text-sm mt-2 p-0 list-none space-y-1">
                            <li>→ React & Tailwind CSS</li>
                            <li>→ Custom WordPress Development</li>
                            <li>→ Shopify & Webflow</li>
                            <li>→ GSAP Animations</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2>Why "Shivrajsinh Zala"?</h2>
                <p>
                    In an industry flooded with copy-paste developers, <strong>Shivrajsinh Zala</strong> stands out by offering a bespoke approach. When businesses in Gujarat or across the globe need an e-commerce store that loads instantly or a portfolio that demands attention, they look for developers who understand both the aesthetic and the engineering.
                </p>
                
                <h2>Connect with Shivrajsinh Zala</h2>
                <p>
                    You can explore more of his work, dive into his open-source code, or view his professional history on the platforms below:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/shivrajsinh-zala/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Connect with Shivrajsinh Zala on LinkedIn</a></li>
                    <li><strong>Instagram:</strong> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/shivrajsinh.sh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Follow Shivrajsinh.sh on Instagram</a></li>
                    <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/shivrajsinhzala" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View Shivrajsinh Zala's Repositories</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t-4 border-black text-center">
                <a href="/#contact" class="inline-block brutal-border bg-brutal-black text-white px-8 py-4 font-mono font-bold hover:bg-[#00FF88] hover:text-black transition-colors shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#000]">
                    HIRE SHIVRAJSINH ZALA →
                </a>
            </div>

        </article>
    </main>

    
    <HumanRedirect />
</Layout>
